comment_data.body: Let's check some settings to see why this error could occur. I want to know how the Dart SDK and Flutter SDK are configured, and the modules in your project. Dart SDK, in Preferences: Flutter SDK, in Preferences: Project Structure, from the File menu: If you can attach similar screen shots we might have a clue. Thanks!
And one more question: Does this happen every time you open the project?

Without additional information we're unfortunately not sure how to resolve this issue. We're going to close this bug for now, but please don't hesitate to comment on the bug if you have any more information for us; we're happy to reopen. Thanks for your contribution!

title: IDE error when I open an existing flutter project in IntelliJ
